strings:
<voice_0x01001118><se_def>Cash: THERE you are!
I've been waiting for you!

<voice_0x01001119><se_def>Cash: Carrie's already inside.
If we hurry, we might be able to catch her!
<voice_0x0100111A><se_def>Cash: Listen, I can't lose. This is my chance to teach her to respect her older brother!

<voice_0x0100111B><se_high>Carrie: Man! Where have you guys BEEN?
I was starting to think you'd never show up!

<voice_0x0100111C><se_high>Carrie: Cash's already inside.
We've got to go after him!
<voice_0x0100111D><se_high>Carrie: I've got to win. I swear, Cash, I'm gonna have you begging for mercy...
